<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="21721509" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="婷婷" data-entry-url="/question/268220653/answer/490037469">

<textarea hidden class="content">&lt;p&gt;国服公孙离了解一下。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;视频链接：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//weibo.com/tv/v/4280467558448805%3Ffid%3D1034%3A4280467558448805&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Sina Visitor System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;视频作者：微博@王者荣耀排行榜&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;视频出处：微博&lt;/p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;video-box&quot; href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/1023169318749687808&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-video-id=&quot;&quot; data-video-playable=&quot;true&quot; data-name=&quot;&quot; data-poster=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-1a523c9d6f41847d7af2d4abf37bb78b_b.jpg&quot; data-lens-id=&quot;1023169318749687808&quot;&gt;              &lt;img class=&quot;thumbnail&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-1a523c9d6f41847d7af2d4abf37bb78b_b.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;                &lt;span class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-ico-extern-gray&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-ico-extern-blue&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;                &lt;span class=&quot;url&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-ico-video&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;https://www.zhihu.com/video/1023169318749687808&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;/span&gt;            &lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;这个视频之前在《装逼成功是什么样的体验》下发过一次啊，不过我感觉和这个标题更加贴切。纯属逗乐。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;婷某人的主页 &lt;a class=&quot;member_mention&quot; href=&quot;//www.zhihu.com/people/fa56b8a0d695d574ba54b5bf9c61f793&quot; data-hash=&quot;fa56b8a0d695d574ba54b5bf9c61f793&quot; data-hovercard=&quot;p$b$fa56b8a0d695d574ba54b5bf9c61f793&quot;&gt;@婷婷&lt;/a&gt; 。还有很多精彩视频。记得关注啊。哈哈哈哈。&lt;/p&gt;</textarea>


<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">

国服公孙离了解一下。视频链接：<a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//weibo.com/tv/v/4280467558448805%3Ffid%3D1034%3A4280467558448805" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Sina Visitor System</a>视频作者：微博@王者荣耀排行榜视频出处：微博这个视频之前在《装逼成功是什么样的体验》下发过一次啊，不过我感觉和这个标题更加贴切。纯属逗乐。婷某人的主页 <a class="member_mention" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/fa56b8a0d695d574ba54b5bf9c61f793" data-hash="fa56b8a0d695d574ba54b5bf9c61f793" data-hovercard="p$b$fa56b8a0d695d574ba54b5bf9c61f793">@婷婷</a> 。还有很多精彩视频。记得关注啊。…

