<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="26806958" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="元气少女只玩亚瑟" data-entry-url="/question/290384745/answer/469631228">

<textarea hidden class="content">&lt;p&gt;这个回答纯属是写着玩的，我也没想到会有这么多人感兴趣，然后你们就当一个搞笑帖看吧，真正实践起来还是有待改进的&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;分割线……&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;以下为原回答……&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;首先你要有家长群的群号&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3559584727d9cb6a45ccb94b18c6ccf1_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;529&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;374&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-7675ba2d56b826cc842acb74be4ceabe_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;529&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3559584727d9cb6a45ccb94b18c6ccf1_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;然后把网名换成这种：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;人生如茶&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;细品岁月&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;大漠祥云&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;金色枫叶&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;花自芬芳&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;幸福女人&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;别样别样&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;枫叶落落&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;简简单单&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;随心而动&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;滴水穿石&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;沁水百合&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;闲云野鹤&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;我心依旧 ……&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;接着就把头像换成这种&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-172be5bb3a8da69f4cde2af1c10a9e95_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;600&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;600&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b8d378e4911d3c2b850b2bb0550940ad_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-172be5bb3a8da69f4cde2af1c10a9e95_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-88e6c3dfcfa5d93d96e8a4fc4ea032f6_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;640&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f9127929ab33590d8b7e760dc119955c_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-88e6c3dfcfa5d93d96e8a4fc4ea032f6_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-e031338a744a9e1131f2b73368370416_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;640&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-228848a1de5b485657d9585e39fc096c_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-e031338a744a9e1131f2b73368370416_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-99a9242077102c1d737fc44faf0348d8_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;798&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;798&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b146cd6af6d6e89df2c95d14c557bdb8_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;798&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-99a9242077102c1d737fc44faf0348d8_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-58689ba3919212da5bd0b43d68b36e5c_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;342&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;342&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-58226b9aaa5fd8c633438d569ed561f9_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;342&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a2e76ce6c5af4f2aec28201496629b81_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;582&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;584&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6e6ee354a8cb725aa07342656c9bb51e_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;582&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a2e76ce6c5af4f2aec28201496629b81_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figu